[Matters](https://support.clio.com/hc/en-us/articles/203337120-Anatomy-of-a-Matter) in Clio represent a firm’s cases. All relevant information—Bills, Documents, Time Entries, etc.—are contained in the Matter. A user’s ability to access a Matter is controlled by the [Matter Permission settings](https://support.clio.com/hc/en-us/articles/203128174-Matter-Permissions-and-Groups). A user without permission will be unable to view or update a Matter.

[Support Link](https://support.clio.com/hc/en-us/articles/218242528-Comprehensive-Guide-Matters#p0)

[Matters in Clio](http://app.clio.com/matters)

